===Pronunciation===
*λογίζομαι / logizomai / log-id'-zom-ahee
=== Etymology ===

*Middle voice from [[λόγος]] {{GG|3056}}; to take an inventory, that is, estimate (literally or figuratively): 
=== Verb ===
conclude, (ac-) count (of), + despise, [[esteem]], impute, lay, number, [[reason]], [[reckon]], suppose, [[think]] (on).